data.title: THREE PIECE PUZZLE
data.meta_description: Indisputably one of the most chilled out hip hop kats in our galaxy! Jneiro Jarel is the man with the next master plan. Are you ready? Well ready or not, he is bringing the hot joints that make you want to bob your head, snap your fingers, and just get your groove on. Born in Brooklyn, he moved to Houston, Texas, at the age of 5. Some years ago he moved back to NYC and more
